---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 relative">
		<!-- About Section -->
		<section class="mb-14 bg-vero-card rounded-lg py-5 px-6 shadow-warm border border-vero-border animate-fade-in">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-normal mb-5 text-vero-text font-serif" style="letter-spacing: -0.025em;">Joe Vero</h1>
			<p class="text-base text-vero-text-mid leading-relaxed mb-4" style="line-height: 1.8;">
				I am a PhD student in the Department of Psychology at Rutgers University. My research interests are in the area of motor control and human movement. I primarily use consumer-grade sensors to study human movement and motor control.
			</p>
			<p class="text-base text-vero-text leading-relaxed" style="line-height: 1.8;">
				I am interested in understanding how humans control their movement and how this control is influenced by the environment. I am also interested in understanding how humans control their movement in typical and atypical populations.
			</p>
		</section>

		<!-- Blog Posts Section -->
		<section class="pt-2 animate-slide-up">
			<h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-vero-text-muted mb-6">Recent Posts</h2>
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<!-- Blog Post Entry -->
				<article class="group border border-vero-border rounded-lg p-5 bg-vero-card shadow-warm card-hover relative overflow-hidden">
					<a href="/blog/first-post" class="block">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-normal text-vero-text group-hover:text-vero-accent transition-colors font-serif mb-2">
							What I did for my master's thesis
						</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-vero-text-mid leading-relaxed mb-3" style="line-height: 1.8;">
							A study of motor control using an interactive Connect the Dots task.
							Explore how humans execute precise movements under varying cognitive load, and what that means for characterizing neurological disorders.
						</p>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs text-vero-text-muted">
							<time datetime="2025-10-25">25 Oct 2025</time>
							<span>&middot;</span>
							<span>Interactive</span>
						</div>
					</a>
				</article>

				<!-- Placeholder for future posts -->
				<article class="group border border-vero-border rounded-lg p-5 opacity-50 bg-vero-card relative overflow-hidden">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-normal mb-2 text-vero-text-muted font-serif">
						Coming Soon: What I am doing for my PhD thesis!
					</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-vero-text-muted mb-3" style="line-height: 1.8;">
						Exploring how humans control their movement in an unsupervised setting with visual feedback.
					</p>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		min-height: 100vh;
	}
</style>
